    </div>

    <!-- SECTION 5 -->
    <h2>5. The Emotional Benefit of a Morning Reset</h2>

    <p>Your morning reset becomes a daily message to yourself:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>“I deserve a calm start.”</li>
      <li>“I don’t need to rush.”</li>
      <li>“I can take things one step at a time.”</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      When practiced consistently, this ritual doesn’t just organize your day —  
      **it changes how you treat yourself**.
    </p>

    <p>
      And that emotional shift is what creates real, long-term productivity.
    </p>

